  <section class="about-card intro-card">
    <div class="about-card-title">
      <h2>hello hello ♡</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card-inner">
      <p>
        I’m Frogs, Froggy, Violet, and probably a few other names depending on
        where you know me from. My legal name is Violet, but because I am
        completely and hopelessly obsessed with frogs, everyone just started
        calling me Frogs. Honestly? I accept my fate.
      </p>

      <p>
        I’m 25, I use <strong>she/her</strong> pronouns, and this website is my
        cosy little pond on the internet. It is full of shrines, collections,
        games, music, memories, and whatever else my brain decides is important
        enough to lovingly archive.
      </p>

      <p class="ribbit-note">
        I like making tiny spaces for the things I care about. This site is one
        of them.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

